Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷一般之巨大蛋糕！混乱的恋爱逃避行！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.81,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生奶油追加一吨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压啊 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 派对可是从傍晚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没让了子发觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 已照您指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有派对 诸星一定会到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他找了子我可受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 哥哥开新年派对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.23,0:02:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正秘密准备中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把我一脚踢开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的飞磨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾有赌此命欲告知之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日午后八时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂家第三号别馆旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于蛋糕层上教堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三号别馆旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于蛋糕层上教堂等候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小终 你的挑战书我接到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位欢迎到面堂家的新年舞会来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么招待的 但尽情的享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是只有在照片中看过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫栗金团是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知该说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱七八糟的盛大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想带点回去给我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种小家子气的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是放任面堂那种人的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们二年四班无产阶级者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须更崇高 圣洁地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些资本家的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这盐味最受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这柱子是软蛋糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说会场是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巨大的蛋糕里头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会想些无意义的事做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对一般大众而言无法了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷 了子小姐请上的杂煮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望和客人们一起用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请人搬杂煮来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是了子已发觉这新年会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这绝不会是平常的杂煮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放毒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像炸弹放在里头也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星 赐你持毒之职
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子 怎么会放毒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子小姐是温柔的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以什么根据在说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.19,0:06:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃的杂煮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把Cherry杂煮搬来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比放毒还糟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有放毒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:07:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子我将和飞磨先生 在甜点教会举行婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说那小飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小终 我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把首级洗净等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是了子小姐为何想举行婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是怨没被邀请到这派对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样就想举行婚礼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.78,0:07:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也许是小飞强逼结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子不会瞒着我举行婚礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全忘了了子的个性了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之不能放着了子不管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何要破坏婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就和了子在甜点教会结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 诸星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你称心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在事情进展前得阻止小飞才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加小飞追击队之人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会出压岁钱的如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一封这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要打扰结婚典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.92,0:08:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近我安装了地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地雷？什么样程度的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女孩子的恶作剧嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应不是什么大规模的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方可是面堂的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想压岁钱加御节料理一年份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及三克拉的钻石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不用担心 有地雷探测器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯亮的地方就是有地雷之处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布满地雷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子怎么做这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶作剧也要有分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子要走就是不太好走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以像我们去换衣服不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:09:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要结婚的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果像那样打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对新娘的了子太无礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 可要十分小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这路上可是到处是地雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说小飞通过的路是不能用咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么阶梯或密道吗？面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是会在蛋糕里做阶梯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不合常理之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是在奇怪的地方合乎常理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令就这样前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点像老鼠的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:21.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软蛋糕内 无法辨认方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃 吃 不停地吃的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开通了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 终于开通了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是青春的一小页
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将永远会被旅行人之流传下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底要做傻事到几时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 这边这边 非常好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是以\N《汉赛尔与格莱特》为蓝图而制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂果然有梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小木偶好像也喜欢有梦想的面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧妙的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 小飞出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用卑鄙的招术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正正当当决胜负如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这陷阱一定是了子弄的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小终
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飞 你藏匿之所我们知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个男人出来作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说你早被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所爱的飞磨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将背弃兄长投向你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于出…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生 请不要为我争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我的决心绝不改变
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然这么为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决心为飞磨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与哥哥断绝关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举行婚礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子 总算下了决心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才过新年 就对我妹妹动手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胆子真大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说些什么弄不懂的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别装了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也不让你和了子结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于我和了子间的关系了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就没把你当问题看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飞 今天今日一定要作个了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 飞磨先生 趁现在逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生 快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 为什么我们两个要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候还说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该了解我的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑 小飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 不要再让了子痛苦好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要逃到何时 小飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.91,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算是了结的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒小终
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒小终
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人怜悯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍着非人的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是为了打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当真 小飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了 见你的诚心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是打倒我之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等小终
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无需多言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的话不假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将打倒你 获取了子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么疯言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂无需多言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥振作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮地倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星先生 为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了约定吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须和打倒面堂之人在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:18:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 这样下去 你会成为拉姆的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是命运的捉弄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手 脖子会被拉长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了了子不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 诸星先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小终 你居然暗算 卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然为救我而舍身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么快粘着他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小飞想要了子就站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我要了子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在怎么反悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将了子拐骗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在这蛋糕屋举行婚礼的还说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是接了小终你的挑战书来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑战书？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说些无聊的理由 小飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然借重了子之力 卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫什么救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险 会被石头拌到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够…够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:20:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞磨先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直相信你会回头的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受这种折磨还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好个诚心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解了小飞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说不要了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对了子的温柔 我实在服了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才看了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子进入地雷的时间控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.01,0:21:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 安歇的时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 管家已经这时候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.93,0:22:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.74,0:23:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥们怎么了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.66,0:23:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了子你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.50,0:23:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请安歇…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========预告===========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我及达令 终太郎 阿忍所乘坐的B-29
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因燃料用尽坠落在南太平洋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那等着我们四人的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.30,0:24:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔境转生 达令在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.45,0:24:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========注===========
